short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically skip ads after X seconds

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is NOT an Ad Blocker, It just closes faster.
Support YouTubers by disabling AdBlock / uBlock on youtube.com and use this extension to skip the ads as soon as possible after the Skip button is available.

Feature: Automatically mute video ads (Changeable on Options)
Feature: Disable / Enable the extension by pressing F2 (Changeable on Options)
New Feature: Change the video's ad playback speed (Changeable on Options until 16x)

This is not an YouTube official extension.

Open Source: https://github.com/ZionDevelopers/youtube-ad-auto-skip
